---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Contact | Oregon Motorcycle Rental"
  description="Contact Oregon Motorcycle Rentals via phone or email to set up a singletrack experience. We have enduro motorcycles from KTM and Husqvarna for rent."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="section-label">Get in Touch</p>
      <h1 class="display page-title">Contact</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact-body">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="contact-grid">

        <div class="contact-main">
          <h2 class="display section-heading">Reservations</h2>
          <p>Call Doug at <a href="tel:5092810156" class="highlight">509-281-0156</a> for questions about dirt bike rentals, training, riding locations, or to make your reservation.</p>
          <p class="deposit-note">If you can't ride on your confirmed reservation date we'll roll any deposit over to a future date at your convenience. You won't lose your deposit if you can't ride on that date!</p>

          <h2 class="display section-heading">Location Dates</h2>
          <p>We're now located year-round in Wickenburg, near Phoenix, Arizona.</p>
        </div>

        <aside class="contact-sidebar">
          <div class="contact-card">
            <p class="section-label">You Should Be Out Riding</p>
            <a href="tel:5092810156" class="phone-number">509-281-0156</a>
            <a href="mailto:gorgemaster@gmail.com" class="email-link">gorgemaster@gmail.com</a>
            <div class="contact-details">
              <p>Doug McDonald<br>56550 Rancho Casitas Road<br>Wickenburg, AZ 85390</p>
              <p>Licensed, bonded, and insured.<br>Se habla Español.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </aside>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); padding: 72px 0 80px; }
  .page-title { font-size: clamp(56px, 9vw, 112px); color: var(--cream); }

  .contact-body { padding: 80px 0; }
  .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start; }

  .section-heading { font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 44px); color: var(--leather); margin: 48px 0 16px; }
  .section-heading:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .contact-main p { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .highlight { color: var(--rust); font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }
  .deposit-note { font-size: 16px; padding: 16px 20px; background: var(--cream-deep); border-left: 3px solid var(--rust); margin-bottom: 48px; }

  .contact-card { border: 2px solid var(--line); padding: 32px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .phone-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Big Shoulders Display', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 36px;
    color: var(--rust);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin: 8px 0;
  }
  .phone-number:hover { color: var(--leather); }
  .email-link { display: block; font-weight: 700; color: var(--leather); text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .email-link:hover { color: var(--rust); }
  .contact-details p { font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 8px; opacity: 0.75; }

  .social-block { margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .social-list { list-style: none; margin: 12px 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; font-size: 15px; }
  .social-list a { color: var(--rust); font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }
  .social-list a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .hashtag { font-size: 15px; margin-top: 12px; }

  .reviews-block {}
  .review-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-top: 12px; }
  .review-links .btn { text-align: center; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
  }
</style>
